Package: ithir
Type: Package
Title: Tools and Data for Digital Soil Informatics
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-05-20
Author: Brendan Malone [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Brendan Malone <brendan.malone@csiro.au>
Description: Provides tools and datasets to support digital soil mapping and analysis workflows. Includes fast mass-preserving spline functions for raster and profile data, model evaluation metrics for both continuous and categorical predictions, and example datasets for demonstration and testing.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: methods, terra
Suggests: MASS, sf, graphics, stats, utils, testthat
